Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Brand New EOT and Bathroom Facilities
Existing fit outs suitable for repurpose

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
30 Delhi Street, West Perth is a modern four level office building located opposite Harold Boas Gardens and within 200 metres of City West Train Station.

The building has received significant refurbishment works and provides a high level of tenant amenity, including;

- Brand new End of Trip facilities including showers, lockers, towel service, drying cupboard and secure bicycle parking;
- Full height glazing availing parkland views to all floors and CBD skyline views from the upper floors;
- On-site facilities management; and,
- High car parking availability.
-Brand new ground floor lobby

Immediate Availability:

Level 3 - NOW FULLY LEASED

Level 2 - 1,191.3sqm: Fully fitted tenancy featuring 2 x boardrooms, 3 x meeting rooms, 2 x quiet rooms, kitchen/breakout area, open plan workstations and storage/utilities. 

Level 1 - 1,191.3sqm: Fully fitted tenancy featuring 4 x meeting rooms, 2 x quiet rooms, kitchen/breakout area, open plan workstations and storage/utilities.  

Ground Floor - 529sqm: Fully refurbished ground floor tenancy with excellent natural light and external terrace. 

This whole building opportunity of 4,460sqm is located adjacent to 1 Campbell Street and connected via a sky bridge, providing the ability to offer up to 5,578sqm.

Outgoings are currently estimated at $156.91/sqm for the 2021/22 financial year.

For any queries, please contact the joint agents.
